        "name": "Attacked From Within",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You assert your power over the target\u2019s own spirit as you reach deep into its soul in order to discover a moment of excruciating anguish, debilitating humiliation, or abject despair. The target takes 12d8 spirit damage and must attempt a Will save.",
